        {
            "title": "今日我咁睇｜存儲芯片概念續跌 利好科網股反彈 惟港股難企穩23000 ｜小編苟豪",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/SPPuj6WZ8ENCVUlT2P0kvQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/bossmind_356/e9e8b9fd1eb136f8d1e654575ed3e326\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">1. 臉書傳出售部分算力，反映科網無限燒錢的故事難以持續，不單急炒上的存儲概念，近年一直強勢的芯片股亦見回調，甚至中國的同行亦避不曹下跌，在壞消息頻頻出來後，小心整個板塊都有較大的調整。<br/>2. 當然，AI上游成本下降，對一直燒錢的科網是好事，因此近月跑輸的微軟、谷歌等，有望有較明顯的反彈，放到港股，則是燒錢發展AI的阿里巴巴等，都有望反彈。這類股份佔指數的比例較高，有望支持大市。<br/>3. 不過，過去的結構性牛市是由AI發展，假如現時故事改為科網企業不再燒錢，那麼AI的升市亦難以持久，整體大市難以靠科網「慳錢」而炒上，大家還是小心為上</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-16cfcb48-8f6e-3acf-a1c2-d1a7e2c994c4-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">。<br/>4.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">早前提過，港股要有所反彈，一是美國不能加息，二是中國經濟是回穩，三是中美關係要好，四是科網股能交出「AI令盈利上升」的證據，美國加息憂慮略減，但其後三個因素仍需觀察。<br/>5. 恒指牛熊證街貨比例，牛證街貨比例屬在低位53%，若牛證低企一段較長時間，或有機會夾上殺熊。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E6%88%91%E5%92%81%E7%9D%87-%E5%AD%98%E5%84%B2%E8%8A%AF%E7%89%87%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E7%BA%8C%E8%B7%8C-%E5%88%A9%E5%A5%BD%E7%A7%91%E7%B6%B2%E8%82%A1%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%88-%E6%83%9F%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E9%9B%A3%E4%BC%81%E7%A9%A923000-%E5%B0%8F%E7%B7%A8%E8%8B%9F%E8%B1%AA-020000444.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 10:07:01",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美伊談判進展及供應充裕拖累油價下跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/i6o7vyqJUYoDXpJdAO_Ydw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEE5S1ZM_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 週四油價下跌，交易員持續評估中東原油供應風險緩解的影響，供應前景改善令市場承壓，儘管地緣政治不確定性仍未完全消散。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國東部時間下午8:16(北京時間次日上午8:16)，美國西德克薩斯中質原油(WTI)期貨下跌0.85%，報每桶68.00美元。布倫特原油期貨尚未開始交易。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國高級官員表示，與伊朗的談判正取得進展，儘管磋商仍處於早期階段，但這已緩解了市場對局勢立即升級、進而干擾波斯灣原油出口的擔憂。與此同時，經由霍爾木茲海峽的原油運輸量已攀升至每日逾1,000萬桶，顯示市場對供應持續穩定流通的信心日益增強，儘管地緣政治風險依然存在。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>供應憂慮緩解，市場靜待新催化劑</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場對波斯灣出口不受干擾的信心持續增強，令油價承壓。近幾週來，霍爾木茲海峽的原油流量穩步回升，而替代方案亦協助恢復了地區主要產油國的出口，緩解了市場對供應長期受衝擊的擔憂。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-da5025ba-3297-3804-82e5-eb7207b41cae-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時，美國能源資訊署(EIA)最新數據顯示，美國國內原油產量於4月份創下每日1,393萬桶的歷史新高，進一步強化了全球供應充裕的預期。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳新銀行(ANZ)表示，華盛頓與德黑蘭達成持久協議的前景改善，已緩解供應方面的憂慮，但霍爾木茲海峽未來管治問題的不確定性，仍為油價提供一定的底部支撐。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管近期油價走軟，但隨著談判持續，交易員仍保持謹慎。市場目前密切關注美伊談判的進一步進展、波斯灣航運的最新動向，以及即將公布的美國庫存與需求數據，以尋求油價走向的更明確指引。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>報導：Roushni Nair</em></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E9%80%B2%E5%B1%95%E5%8F%8A%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E5%85%85%E8%A3%95%E6%8B%96%E7%B4%AF%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C-012702494.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 09:36:51",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "北方之星任命新行政總裁及主席，應對Elliott維權股東施壓",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Linaol8dBpjX_6D2P1VUNg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA6H0CU_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 澳洲最大黃金礦商北方之星資源公司（ASX:NST）週二宣布，任命Suresh Vadnagra接替Stuart Tonkin出任下一任行政總裁，此舉正值維權投資者向該公司施壓、要求全面改革管理層之際。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">北方之星在聲明中表示，Vadnagra來自總部位於倫敦的嘉能可（LON:GLEN），將於10月5日正式上任。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">公司另發聲明稱，Michael Ashforth將於11月股東週年大會後接替Michael Chaney出任主席一職。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-23c7c910-9325-333f-b182-ef42ba805099-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次領導層變動，源於維權投資機構Elliott Investment Management上月披露持有北方之星逾10億澳元（6.890億美元）的股份，並公開呼籲公司全面改革董事會、提升股東價值。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Elliott此前指出，北方之星股價長期表現欠佳，並要求公司推行大刀闊斧的改革以改善回報。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">北方之星股價2026年迄今已累跌23%，走勢與過去三個月金價的下滑趨勢一致。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8C%97%E6%96%B9%E4%B9%8B%E6%98%9F%E4%BB%BB%E5%91%BD%E6%96%B0%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E7%B8%BD%E8%A3%81%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-%E6%87%89%E5%B0%8Delliott%E7%B6%AD%E6%AC%8A%E8%82%A1%E6%9D%B1%E6%96%BD%E5%A3%93-005306273.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 08:56:34",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美股期貨持穩，投資者靜待就業數據並關注伊朗談判進展",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Linaol8dBpjX_6D2P1VUNg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA6H0CU_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com — 美國股指期貨於週三晚間小幅波動，此前華爾街在震盪行情中收低。投資者正密切等待備受關注的6月非農就業報告，以尋找聯準會政策走向的線索。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間下午8:45（北京時間週四上午8:45），標普500指數期貨微跌0.1%至7,536.0點，納斯達克100指數期貨下滑0.1%至30,068.75點，道指期貨同樣下跌0.1%至52,600.0點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國主要股指在第三季度首個交易日均以下跌收場。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3402a3dd-dc52-3b29-8467-67c9fc05b159-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">道瓊斯工業平均指數小幅下滑，標普500指數跌0.2%，納斯達克綜合指數則重挫0.7%，主要受半導體及人工智能相關股票大幅下跌拖累。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場持續聚焦利率前景。聯準會主席凱文·沃什（Kevin Warsh）重申央行致力於將通膨率壓回2%目標，儘管他同時指出近期通膨預期已有所緩和。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場目光現已轉向週四公布的非農就業報告。由於獨立紀念日假期，該報告將比往常提前一天發布。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">經濟學家預計，美國6月新增就業人數約為11.4萬，低於5月的17.2萬。投資者正密切關注勞動市場降溫的跡象，這將對聯準會的下一步行動產生重要影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">地緣政治局勢同樣備受關注。美國與伊朗談判代表於週三在多哈結束了為期兩天的間接談判。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次談判主要圍繞霍爾木茲海峽的海上通行及伊朗凍結資產的解凍問題展開，這兩項議題均是上月達成的臨時協議的核心內容。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原油價格在亞洲週一交易時段進一步回落，有助於緩解近幾週令市場動盪的通膨憂慮。投資者愈發將油價走勢與中東局勢緊張程度，與通膨預期及貨幣政策走向緊密掛鉤。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管週三出現回調，美國股市仍維持在歷史高位附近，此前第二季度錄得強勁漲幅。投資者目前正在高估值與經濟韌性及持續盈利增長預期之間審慎權衡。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E6%9C%9F%E8%B2%A8%E6%8C%81%E7%A9%A9-%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%80%85%E9%9D%9C%E5%BE%85%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E4%B8%A6%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E9%80%B2%E5%B1%95-015700137.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 10:07:02",
